properties.abstract: Lush green flower meadows, fascinating fauna, an emerald green mountain lake with temperatures as high as 23 degrees and a fantastic view of the mountains  you'll find it all in the village of Lungern.
properties.description:
One of the nicest bicycle trails is the one leading around the lake; its both easy and exciting. You start in Obsee, right next to the Lungern-Turren-Bahn station. This is also where youll find the Brnig Indoor shooting center. In June and July you can see more than 100 types of butterflies in the nature paradise of Brnig-West.

After you pass Kaiserstuhl and Brglen, youll see the Dundelsbach waterfall. The two-level fall is definitely worth a closer look. Its under national protection.
